PROGRAMMER'S KEYBOARD READ ME

Use of the program is best implemented in the current condition on a Macintosh computer running the mac OS. In order to use the program the pynput module of python must be active on the computer

In order to make the long press functionality work on a mac the user must go to the system preferences, and then once there click on keyboard. From here the user should  move the "Delay Until Repeat" slider to long. 

Attempts to implement the funcitons on WIndows computer's were not met with much success. An dat current development no method is known that will properly allow for the functionality